    narr:generatedFrom "d1b09a828565de86" ;
    narr:narration """This hub gathers per-conversation and per-artifact scorings on one rubric dimension — does the material advance the strategy? Across [YC application alignment](narr:Assessment_StrategicAlignment_YC), the [narrative-architecture through-line](narr:RubricAssess_StrategicAlignment), the [founder career-arc artifact](narr:Rubric_StrategicAlignment_ScarletDame), and the [pilot plan](narr:Rubric_StrategicAlignment_PilotPlan), the recurring anchor is collective memory / 'narrative as steering vector' as both story and product thesis. GTM threads run through [consultant-led pricing and tiers](narr:RubricAssess_Strategy_GTM), the [side-door demo motion](narr:RubricAssess_StrategicAlignment_Sample1), and [revenue/TAM with the GitHub analogy](narr:Assess_Strategy_RevenueModelTAM). Segmentation and ICP appear in the [architecture-teams beachhead](narr:RubricAssess_StrategicAlignment_WeeklyCall) and the [a founder beta user call](narr:Rubric_StrategicAlignment_FounderBetaUser), which surfaces a new operations persona and a VC channel. Enterprise dimensions — on-prem, cross-platform, AI-to-AI provenance — enter via the [the customer's chief architect call](narr:Rubric_StrategicAlignment_CustomerArchitect). YC-specific framing recurs in [demo beats](narr:Rubric_StrategicAlignment_YCDemoBeats) and the [YC call](narr:Rubric_StrategicAlignment_YC_Call). Every child here scores high alignment; the rubric records no misalignment instance, so divergence lives in *what* each aligns toward, not whether it aligns.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Assess_Strategy_RevModel> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Assess_Strategy_RevenueModelTAM> ;
